videos.description: Victor Bolden Jr. zigs and zags his way for 17 yds and a 1st down
videos.headline: Beaver travels a long way for 17 yard gain

videos.description: Ryan Nall runs for 89 yd TD
videos.headline: 89 yard TD run puts OSU up 7-0

videos.description: Marcus McMaryion pass complete to Ryan Nall for 19 yd TD
videos.headline: Beavers up 14-0 after TD pass

videos.description: Oregon State goes to the bag of tricks when Seth Collins takes the direct snap, pitches it back to Marcus McMaryion and then gets the forward pass back to him as he scampers in from 46 yards to the Beavers touchdown.
videos.headline: Collins takes the snap and then makes the TD catch for Oregon State

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Tavares Martin Jr. for 33 yd TD as OSU now leads 21-6
videos.headline: Washington State cuts into lead with TD pass

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Jamal Morrow for 66 yds and a TD as OSU now leads 24-14
videos.headline: 66 yard TD pass gets WSU closer

videos.description: In a jump ball at the goal line, Gabe Marks leaps the highest and steals what looks like an interception and turns it into a 37-yard touchdown for Washington State to get the Cougars closer at 24-21.
videos.headline: Marks steals away the pick for incredible TD

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Gabe Marks for 28 yd TD to take 28-24 lead
videos.headline: Cougars take 1st lead after Falk's 4th TD pass of game

videos.description: Ryan Nall runs for 3 yd TD as OSU takes a 31-28 lead
videos.headline: Ryan Nall's 3rd TD puts Oregon State back ahead

videos.description: Luke Falk pass complete to Robert Lewis for 1 yd TD as WSU goes up 35-31
videos.headline: Washington State regains lead with short TD pass
